{"root":{"data":{"id":"djin8axefug0","created":1782442775759,"text":"测铜绿微囊藻昼夜 pH 曲线"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djin8unq1ww0","created":1782442818709,"text":"铜绿微囊藻正常培养\n↓\n12 h 光 / 12 h 暗\n↓\n用 pH 计每 2–4 h 测一次 bulk pH\n↓\n连续测 2–3 个昼夜周期\n↓\n得到真实 pH 曲线"},"children":[]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}